item.description: Wire Tool V1.1 User Manual (UNDER CONSTRUCTION AS OF 25.09.07. DO NOT USE.) What is the Wire Tool V1.1? The Wire Tool V1.1 is simplified and improved open-source wire EDM (electrical discharge machining) wire EDM toolhead developed by Rack Robotics. It aims to provide a cost-effective and easily hackable solution for wire EDM enthusiasts and professionals. The Wire Tool V1.1 is designed to be mounted to a CNC motion system of the user’s choice.
